(42, 22, 70, 40, 27, 11, 11, NULL, 'Jesus'' Identity Affirmation', 'Both passages emphasize Jesus'' affirmation of his identity in response to questions about his divine status. The phrases ''Ye say that I am'' and ''Thou sayest'' highlight a similar structure in how Jesus acknowledges the titles given to him.', 'parallel', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
